Title: ‘Hot Fuzz’ Digital Score Album Released |  Film Music Reporter
Description: Back Lot Music has released a digital version of the score album for Hot Fuzz . The album features the film’s original score composed by David Arnold . The 2007 original soundtrack album featuring songs from the movie was released by Interscope Records .
